articles.title: In Pics | South Korean lunar orbiter Danuri sends images of the Moon and the Earth - Moneycontrol
articles.description: The word Danuri is a portmanteau of the Korean words 'Moon' and 'Enjoy'. It was launched on a SpaceX rocket from the United States of America in August 2022 and entered lunar orbit last month.
